       California Energy Commission

   The energy challenge facing California is real.

   For information on how you can help, click here.

   The State Council on Developmental Disabilities encourages practical
   and feasible energy saving measures while considering the health and
   safety of clients, workers and family members.

   The State Independent Living Council has posted advice for persons with
   disabilities during power shortages on its website. (PDF Document --
   Adobe Acrobat Reader required)


